    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Shield Generator</em></p>\n<p>You modify your shield generator to overload. As an action you can overload your shield. Each Large or smaller creature within 5 feet of you must make a Dexterity or Strength saving throw (their choice). On a failed save, they are pushed back 5 feet and knocked prone.</p>\n<p>You can use this feature twice. You gain an additional use at 5th, 9th, 13th, and 17th level. You regain any expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p>",
